oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Andrews Tabernacle Christian Methodist Episicopal Church
306 Woods Ferry Road, Highway 109, Lebanon, TN

Black and white photograph of a white church with wood siding, gable roof and one-story front porch; porch has double doors with cement stairs leading up to it; stairs have black metal railing; side facade has three rectangle window and air conditioning unit; propane tank visible in background on right
Andrews Tabernacle Christian Methodist Episicopal Church was established in 1897.
